heres what she found about the path of advancement from 
assistant to associate professor 
among those who were married but childless 51 percent of the 
men and 41 percent of the women were promoted 
among those who had spouses and children 66 percent of the men 
and 51 percent of the women were promoted 
among those who were single divorced or widowed and childless 
53 percent of the men and 37 percent of the women were promoted 
