years in prison to death have now been set up in the northwestern 
and central military administrative districts the official radio 
rangoon said tuesday quoting new orders dated aug 2 a transcript 
of the report was available wednesday in bangkok 
the new orders also extended the authority to dispense martial 
law to junior commanders in both areas 
on aug 8 1988 tens of thousands of people took to the streets 
