citys many hills the damage was contained and 70000 died more 
than half the population 
the citys call for steppedup enforcement of a national policy 
banning nuclear warheads including those on us ships at japanese 
ports may command the attention of the government now that the 
governing liberal democrats have been weakened by a series of 
scandals and unpopular policies 
