r higgins and another videotape showing american hostage joseph 
cicippio urging the release of a moslem cleric who was kidnapped by 
israel 
theyve been so offended by that regardless of their view on 
the politics of the middle east or any other area that we are 
finding more and more of a willingness to help bush said 
