other of violating agreements relating to movements of their 
respective troops in the area 
they are trying to humilitate us in our own house said maj 
edgardo lopez grimaldo a spokesman for the defense forces we 
will not be trapped into provocation in order not to respond to 
yankee arrogance 
at the pentagon in washington army maj kathy wood said the 
actions did not violate the panama canal treaties under which 
the commander of a military area of coordination has 
responsibility for the security of his area 
