basic cars of the past that had obvious places for clocks or 
airconditioning units 
in a much larger sense thats what were struggling with on 
how we handle the next generation of platforms he said 
chrysler will be introducing a new basic design in late 1992 for 
the 1993 model year in gales world of designing for the future 
the cars that are built on those platforms are in the works today 
when you get to a world where there are so many things where 
there is so much technology and theres so many models different 
